  "detailed_description": "Lightwave is a platformer project gone full indie. Inspired by classic platformers and modern indie titles alike, this 2D pixel platformer features highspeed, fluid movement.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Follow up the basics of platforming with advanced tech as you jump, slide and dash your way across the different Grids and overcome various obstacles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1521820/extras/6ca9901d1b9c637ab30f779da3975e92.poster.avif?t=1614189604\" width=636 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1521820/extras/6ca9901d1b9c637ab30f779da3975e92.webm?t=1614189604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1521820/extras/6ca9901d1b9c637ab30f779da3975e92.mp4?t=1614189604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Unlock the RGBeam to unlock your true speed potential.<br><br></li><li>Race your friends across the Grid with 4 player split-screen, or if your feeling up to the challenge, set the best times to top the leaderboards!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1521820/extras/ce8cc6cc6cd8214e8f3f403b803afdf3.poster.avif?t=1614189604\" width=436 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1521820/extras/ce8cc6cc6cd8214e8f3f403b803afdf3.webm?t=1614189604\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1521820/extras/ce8cc6cc6cd8214e8f3f403b803afdf3.mp4?t=1614189604\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Enjoy an original chiptune soundtrack full of up upbeat music to race to.<br><br></li><li>Take on the Speedrun mode and complete the game in a single sitting as fast as you can.</li></ul>",
